With 15 years in software development and consulting, Fantech Labs delivers premium solutions. Founded by graduates from Pakistan's top engineering and business schools, our team excels at understanding client needs and providing accurate timelines.

Our services include:

We're committed to high-quality results that meet evolving client demands across various software niches, seamlessly integrating into complex codebases with innovation

description.content:
Are you Looking for a top-notch MERN stack developer to transform your web app vision into a reality? Look no further! I'm here to provide you with expert web development services that are robust and adaptable, harnessing the latest technologies.


I am a dedicated Full Stack Web Developer, well-versed in Node.js, React.js, Express.js, Next.js, and MongoDB. My portfolio speaks volumes, showcasing a consistent track record of delivering exceptional web applications that consistently exceed client expectations.


Here's what I bring to the table:


Web application development using the MERN stack: Harnessing the power of Node.js, React.js, Express.js, and Next.js to craft feature-rich web apps.


Crafting RESTful APIs: Building robust APIs that power your web application and facilitate smooth communication.


Development Approach

  • Project Discussion
  • Design analysis
  • Software Architecture Design
  • Design translation into working App
  • Application Testing across different screen sizes
  • Application Deployment



Portfolio : https://pro.fiverr.com/users/nomi13ok/portfolio?gig=be-your-mean-mern-and-node-full-stack-web-developer&origin=gig_page


Please message me before placing the order

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide UI/UX Designs?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we do provide UI/UX design service for web, mobile apps and AI apps.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work with Node Based Front-end Frameworks?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, we work with Node.js based front-end frameworks like 
Gatsby
Nextjs
Reactjs
Vue

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you also offer backend services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we offer backend services in variety of stacks, namely Python, PHP, Node based frameworks like nuxt.js

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Deployment services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We provide deployment services on different platforms like Azure, AWS, GCP, Vercel etc for additional cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you use CI/CD Approach?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we use CI/CD Approach using Git Actions, Gitlab actions, and also write custom Deployment pipelines for additional cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What Databases you use for web-apps?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We use almost all sorts of DB, both SQL and NO-SQL based database.
